{"profile":{"awsPrograms":[{"category":"Container Hero","joinedAt":2019.0,"memberStatus":"ACTIVE","programName":"HERO"}],"basicInfo":{"alias":"vlaaaaaaad","avatar":"https://avatars.builderprofile.aws.dev/2tpY13mtbdTSchAQ7yPzXt06FZH.webp","bio":"Vlad Ionescu (he/him) jokingly describes himself as a “Professional mistake avoider”, which he argues is a better way of saying “Independent Consultant”. His work is devoted to getting companies to high-performing levels.\n\nVlad swings wildly on the engineer/manager pendulum, and he is always full of energy. As an Individual Contributor, he focuses on architecting resilient applications and on growing engineers. As a Manager, he focuses on empowering people to do their best work and on building sustainable companies.\n\nIn parallel to his tech career, Vlad is a foodie and very much into cocktails, whiskey, and wine — finding him at a tasting or food pairing event is a sure bet. He cherishes mental health and is an avid proponent of any effort in the area.","builderProfileId":"9de04a3f-b63d-4d2e-ac2d-be13a9594785","createdOn":1.715094552576E12,"headline":"Sugarbaby Tech Consultant","isStaff":false,"name":"Vlad Ionescu (he/him)"},"location":{"displayLocation":{"countryRegion":"RO"}},"profileStatus":"ACTIVE","socials":{"blog":"https://www.vladionescu.me","github":"https://github.com/Vlaaaaaaad","linkedIn":"https://www.linkedin.com/in/vlaaaaaaad","twitter":"https://x.com/iamvlaaaaaaad"}}}